description: This Chainlink VRF common Parvati purrs with a rating of 25, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 75, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, Box for East, 2 for South, and Stringalong for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Parvati [75 Votes, Common]
